{{Actor|
| type = Map spot
| name = Point pusher
| class = PointPusher
| doomednum = 5001
}}[[Classes]]: <u>PointPusher</u><br>

A point pusher pushes nearby actors away from it. This force crosses sector boundaries, decreases linearly with distance, and is felt within a circle centered on itself. The force is felt only if the point pusher can see the target object. To pull actors in, see [[Classes:PointPuller|PointPuller]].

The [[sector]] in which the thing is placed must have the “Pusher Enabled” bit set, see [[sector specials]].

